agent_meseret_intro: Ji'a shanaf Poppo Live irratti hojjachaa ture. Ji'aa birrii 100,000 ol argadha.

earn_additional_income_desc: Wanti hojjechuu qabdu ijoo ani agarsiisu hordofuu qofa. Haala kanaan, wabsaayitii kana irratti hojjachuuf qorannoo barnootaa hin barbaachisu, yeroo barbaaddu hojjachuu dandeenya, afaan keenyaan haasawuu dandeenya, namoota biyyaa garaagaraa qunnamuu nuuf danda'aa, kan hojii kana nuuf gammachu taasisa.
opening_options_desc: Play Store irraa dirqisiifaa dhaabbachuu danda'uu irraa kan hafe, karaa filatamaa irraa baneessuudha, kanaaf linkii ani gadi dhiyeenye taphaachuun dhaabbadhaa
choose_what_works_desc: Linkii irraa dhaabbatee booda, akkamitti baneessuu barbaaddu filannoo si agarsiisa. Karaa siif hojjetu filadhu.
the_front_page_desc: Fuula kanaa akka akkaawuntii Poppo Live sirrii ta'een baneessite ni mirkaneessa. Itti aanu fuula ijoo wabsaayitii guddatti deemna. Kunis ikoonii 5ffaa gadi mookii laayitii ykn "O" ðŸ’¡ jedhu taphaachuun dha.
our_next_task_desc: Kun yeroo dhufu "Auth" jedhu taphaachuun odoo jalqabee suuraa kee fi ulfina fuulaa kennuudha. Asii keessatti qopheeffamee jiru, waan inni hojjetu hordofuu qofa. Yeroo ulfina fuulaa kennitu fuula keessaa waan dhuunfatuu hin jiraachuu qabu, fakkeenyaaf, hijab, miidhagaa...
finally_desc: Yeroo "My Agency" jedhu suuraa darbii 4 irraa argamtuu taphaattu, kun mul'ata. Itti aanu "Please enter agent's ID" jedhu taphaachuun "45227747" jedhu galchaa, ergaa asii gadi Temesgen_Agency jedhu taphaachuun dhuma "confirm" jedhu taphaachuun warrii nuuf agarsiifama.
next_step_desc: Warriin kun yeroo ol aanaa mul'atu "Back" jedhu taphaachuun asii dhaabbachuu dandeessa. ID kee galchaa ergaa booda, warrii akka kanaa maqaa kee ol aanaa fi maqaa agentii kee gadi agarsiisu mul'ata. Sana booda, waan homaa hojjachuu baachuu "Back" jedhu taphaachuun baachuu dandeessa.
practical_guidelines_desc: Kana hordofuun sirriitti agentii ta'uu dandeessa.
copy_popo_id: ID Poppo kee profile kee irraa dhaabbadhu
what_is_poppo_live_desc: Poppo Live platformii mediaa hawaasaa addunyaa kan argaa dabalataa argachuuf video call namoota biyyaa garaagaraa waliin haasawuudha. Platformiin kun argaa dabalataa argachuuf carraa gaarii kenna.
how_does_it_work_desc: Poppo Live irratti, video call namoota waliin haasawuudhaan, taphaa taphaachuudhaan fi hawaasa garaagaraa keessatti hirmaachuudhaan koonsii fi kennaa argatta. Koonsiin kun gatii qalamaa ta'ee jijjiiramuu danda'a.
income_collection_methods_desc: Karaalee gurguddoon argachaa qabeenyaa Poppo Live irratti kennaa fudhachuu, video call callii dhiraa, taphaa hirmaachuu fi hojii agentii dabalata. Hojii hunda carraa argachaa qabeenyaa adda addaa kenna.

faq_what_is_poppo_desc: Poppo Live platformii video call addunyaa kan argaa qabeenyaa argachuuf callii gochuudha.
